results.content: Central Stokes. This is Ellie speaking. How can I help?
Hi there. I would like to book a taxi for 03:30, going from Orwellard at 17 Oakwell Place to 22 Corby Park Close at the name of Tam.
Not a problem at all. I'll go ahead and get that booked in just now for you for three-- half past three.
Okay. Lovely. Thank you for your assistance.
